WEBVTT

01:30:09.358 --> 01:30:11.233
Two fellows came here
to sabotage the wedding.

01:30:12.274 --> 01:30:13.274
What?!

01:30:13.358 --> 01:30:14.483
They came in a jeep.

01:30:14.983 --> 01:30:16.108
One of them stayed in the jeep.

01:30:16.108 --> 01:30:17.733
I gave them a piece of my mind
and sent them packing.

01:30:18.108 --> 01:30:19.816
Any idea who they might be?
